  "contentHtml": "\n    \n    \n        \n                <ul>\n                    \n                     <li><a href=\"/news/hospitals\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Hospitals</a></li>                     <li>1 min read</li>                 </ul>\n                            \n        \n                                    \n\n                                                                            <p><img src=\"https://health.economictimes.indiatimes.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/et-default-user.svg\" alt=\"Online Bureau\">\n                                            \n                                        </p>\n                                                                        \n                                                                                    <ul>\n                                                                                                    <li>\n                                                                                                                    <a>Online Bureau</a>\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n                                                                                                            </li>\n                                                                                                                                                    <li><a href=\"/agency/88675629/ETHealthWorld\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ETHealthWorld</a></li>\n                                                                                            </ul>\n                                                                                <ul>\n                                                                                            <li>Published On Mar 19, 2026 at 12:09 PM IST</li>\n                                                                                                                                </ul>\n                                    \n                                                                            \n                                                                        \n                                \n                                \n\n                    <!-- Display video article in news article for the custom next story -->\n                    \n                    <!-- Modifying the body placing embeds,promoslots,related etc.-->\n                                        <figure><img src=\"/images/default.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure> Kolkata: Reinforcing its focus on advanced tertiary care, CK Birla Hospitals CMRI has introduced a next-generation <a href=\"/tag/smart+cochlear+implant+system\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">smart cochlear implant system</a>, marking a key step forward in specialised <a href=\"/tag/ent+care\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ENT care</a> in Eastern India.The procedure was successfully performed by Dr N V K Mohan, highlighting the hospital’s clinical expertise and growing capabilities in handling complex <a href=\"/tag/hearing+restoration\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">hearing restoration</a> cases.<!-- PROMOSLOT_M -->This development underscores CMRI’s continued investment in cutting-edge medical technologies and specialised interventions, particularly in a region where access to advanced hearing solutions has been limited. The focus remains on enhancing patient outcomes through precision-driven procedures and integrated care.\n                            <p>Advt\n                            </p>\n\n                              \n                                                         \n                        With a strong ENT team and the use of advanced tools like SmartNav for accurate implant placement, the hospital is steadily strengthening its position in innovative and future-ready hearing care.                    \n                                                                    \n                                                                \n                                <ul>\n                                                                            <!-- <li>By <span>Online Bureau</span>,</li> -->\n                                    \n\n                                                                            <li>By\n                                                                                            <a>Online Bureau</a>\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                        , \n                                                                                    </li>\n                                                                        <li><a href=\"/agency/88675629/ETHealthWorld\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ETHealthWorld</a></li>\n                                </ul>\n                                <ul>\n                                    <!-- <li> Updated On Mar 19, 2026 at 12:09 PM IST</li> -->\n                                    <li>Published On Mar 19, 2026 at 12:09 PM IST</li>\n                                    <!-- <li class=\"desktop-view\">1 min read</li> -->\n                                </ul>\n                            \n                                        \n\n                    \n\n                    <!-- Comment Section -->\n                    \n                    <!-- Comment Section -->\n\n                    \n                      \n    \n            <p>\n                </p><h2>Join the community of 2M+ industry professionals. </h2>   \n                <h3>Subscribe to Newsletter to get latest insights &amp; analysis in your inbox.</h3>\n            <p></p>\n\n           